      <title>Syrian Refugees Return From Lebanon Only to Flee War Yet Again</title>
      <category domain="https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/crises-conflicts/">Crises &amp; Conflicts</category>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2017 10:41:23 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>Abby Sewell</author>
      <link>https://www.newsdeeply.com/refugees/articles/2017/10/11/syrian-refugees-return-from-lebanon-only-to-flee-war-yet-again</link>
